<heading allCaps="true" bold="true" fontSize="12" level="2" pageId="20" pageNumber="2802" reason="3">
<emphasis bold="true" pageId="20" pageNumber="2802">
DESCRIPTION OF 
<taxonomicName authority="Zheng &amp; Wittouck &amp; Salvetti &amp; Franz &amp; Harris &amp; Mattarelli &amp; O’Toole &amp; Pot &amp; Vandamme &amp; Walter &amp; Watanabe &amp; Wuyts &amp; Felis &amp; Gänzle &amp; Lebeer, 2020" authorityName="Zheng &amp; Wittouck &amp; Salvetti &amp; Franz &amp; Harris &amp; Mattarelli &amp; O’Toole &amp; Pot &amp; Vandamme &amp; Walter &amp; Watanabe &amp; Wuyts &amp; Felis &amp; Gänzle &amp; Lebeer" authorityYear="2020" box="[370,687,184,213]" class="Bacilli" family="Lactobacillaceae" genus="Bombilactobacillus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Bacteria" order="Lactobacillales" pageId="20" pageNumber="2802" phylum="Firmicutes" rank="genus" status="GEN. NOV.">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[370,687,184,213]" italics="true" pageId="20" pageNumber="2802">BOMBILACTOBACILLUS</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[121,262,221,250]" pageId="20" pageNumber="2802" rank="genus">GEN. NOV.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="20" pageNumber="2802" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="20.[120,766,184,885]" pageId="20" pageNumber="2802">
<taxonomicName authorityName="Zheng &amp; Wittouck &amp; Salvetti &amp; Franz &amp; Harris &amp; Mattarelli &amp; O’Toole &amp; Pot &amp; Vandamme &amp; Walter &amp; Watanabe &amp; Wuyts &amp; Felis &amp; Gänzle &amp; Lebeer" authorityYear="2020" box="[121,322,263,287]" class="Bacilli" family="Lactobacillaceae" genus="Bombilactobacillus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Bacteria" order="Lactobacillales" pageId="20" pageNumber="2802" phylum="Firmicutes" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[121,322,263,287]" italics="true" pageId="20" pageNumber="2802">Bombilactobacillus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Bom.bi.lac.to.ba.cil’lus. L. masc. n. 
<emphasis box="[121,201,293,317]" italics="true" pageId="20" pageNumber="2802">bombus</emphasis>
, buzzing of bees and bumblebees, N.L. masc. n. 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Beijerinck" authorityYear="1901" class="Bacilli" family="Lactobacillaceae" genus="Lactobacillus" kingdom="Bacteria" order="Lactobacillales" pageId="20" pageNumber="2802" phylum="Firmicutes" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="20" pageNumber="2802">Lactobacillus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
a bacterial genus; N.L. masc. n. 
<emphasis box="[539,743,324,348]" italics="true" pageId="20" pageNumber="2802">
<taxonomicName authorityName="Zheng &amp; Wittouck &amp; Salvetti &amp; Franz &amp; Harris &amp; Mattarelli &amp; O’Toole &amp; Pot &amp; Vandamme &amp; Walter &amp; Watanabe &amp; Wuyts &amp; Felis &amp; Gänzle &amp; Lebeer" authorityYear="2020" box="[539,739,324,348]" class="Bacilli" family="Lactobacillaceae" genus="Bombilactobacillus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Bacteria" order="Lactobacillales" pageId="20" pageNumber="2802" phylum="Firmicutes" rank="genus">Bombilactobacillus</taxonomicName>
,
</emphasis>
a lactobacillus from bees and bumble bees).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="20" pageNumber="2802" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="20.[120,766,184,885]" pageId="20" pageNumber="2802">
<taxonomicName box="[121,413,401,425]" pageId="20" pageNumber="2802">
<emphasis box="[121,322,401,425]" italics="true" pageId="20" pageNumber="2802">Bombilactobacillus</emphasis>
species
</taxonomicName>
have been isolated from the stomach and the hindgut of honey bees (
<emphasis box="[560,704,431,455]" italics="true" pageId="20" pageNumber="2802">
Apis 
<taxonomicName box="[613,704,431,455]" class="Bacilli" family="Lactobacillaceae" genus="Apilactobacillus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Bacteria" order="Lactobacillales" pageId="20" pageNumber="2802" phylum="Firmicutes" rank="species" species="mellifera">mellifera</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
) and bumble bees where they are associated with the heterofermentative sister genus 
<emphasis box="[374,551,493,517]" italics="true" pageId="20" pageNumber="2802">
<taxonomicName authorityName="Zheng &amp; Wittouck &amp; Salvetti &amp; Franz &amp; Harris &amp; Mattarelli &amp; O’Toole &amp; Pot &amp; Vandamme &amp; Walter &amp; Watanabe &amp; Wuyts &amp; Felis &amp; Gänzle &amp; Lebeer" authorityYear="2020" box="[374,546,493,517]" class="Bacilli" family="Lactobacillaceae" genus="Apilactobacillus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Bacteria" order="Lactobacillales" pageId="20" pageNumber="2802" phylum="Firmicutes" rank="genus">Apilactobacillus</taxonomicName>
.
</emphasis>
<taxonomicName pageId="20" pageNumber="2802">
<emphasis box="[559,760,493,517]" italics="true" pageId="20" pageNumber="2802">Bombilactobacillus</emphasis>
species
</taxonomicName>
have genome sizes which range from 1.81 to 1.84 Mbp and a mol% G+C content ranging from 34.7 to 39.5. They are homofermentative and thermophilic; comparable to other insect-associated lactobacilli, bombilactobacilli ferment only a narrow spectrum of carbohydrates.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="20" pageNumber="2802" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="20.[120,766,184,885]" pageId="20" pageNumber="2802">
A phylogenetic tree on the basis of 16S rRNA genes of all species in the genus 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Zheng &amp; Wittouck &amp; Salvetti &amp; Franz &amp; Harris &amp; Mattarelli &amp; O’Toole &amp; Pot &amp; Vandamme &amp; Walter &amp; Watanabe &amp; Wuyts &amp; Felis &amp; Gänzle &amp; Lebeer" authorityYear="2020" box="[349,550,722,746]" class="Bacilli" family="Lactobacillaceae" genus="Bombilactobacillus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Bacteria" order="Lactobacillales" pageId="20" pageNumber="2802" phylum="Firmicutes" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[349,550,722,746]" italics="true" pageId="20" pageNumber="2802">Bombilactobacillus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is provided in 
<figureCitation captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="7.[185,216,1617,1636]" captionTargetBox="[264,1323,181,1565]" captionTargetId="figure-17@7.[264,1323,181,1565]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="Fig. 6. Gene family presence/absence patterns in Lactobacillaceae and Leuconostocaceae. Each column represents a gene family presence/absence pattern in species of Lactobacillaceae and Leuconostoaceae, where presence is indicated with a dot. The absolute number of gene families that conform to each pattern is visualized in the marginal bar plot at the top. Separations between phylogroups are indicated with horizontal black lines. We defined genes that were present in all genomes of a clade and in none of the genomes outside of that clade as ‘signature genes’ (dark blue); other genes are shown in light blue. Only presence/absence patterns followed by four or more gene families are shown. Patterns of presence in a single species or all species are not shown. Unassigned species are clusters of closely related genomes which could not be assigned to a known species due to low whole-genome similarity to a type strain and/or low 16S rRNA similarity to a type strain." pageId="20" pageNumber="2802">Fig. S6B</figureCitation>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="20" pageNumber="2802" type="type_taxon">
<paragraph blockId="20.[120,766,184,885]" pageId="20" pageNumber="2802">
The 
<typeStatus box="[170,217,799,823]" pageId="20" pageNumber="2802">type</typeStatus>
species is 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Zheng &amp; Wittouck &amp; Salvetti &amp; Franz &amp; Harris &amp; Mattarelli &amp; O’Toole &amp; Pot &amp; Vandamme &amp; Walter &amp; Watanabe &amp; Wuyts &amp; Felis &amp; Gänzle &amp; Lebeer" authorityYear="2020" baseAuthorityName="Zheng &amp; Wittouck &amp; Salvetti &amp; Franz &amp; Harris &amp; Mattarelli &amp; O’Toole &amp; Pot &amp; Vandamme &amp; Walter &amp; Watanabe &amp; Wuyts &amp; Felis &amp; Gänzle &amp; Lebeer" baseAuthorityYear="2020" box="[338,628,799,823]" class="Bacilli" family="Lactobacillaceae" genus="Bombilactobacillus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Bacteria" order="Lactobacillales" pageId="20" pageNumber="2802" phylum="Firmicutes" rank="species" species="mellifer" status="comb. nov">
<emphasis box="[338,628,799,823]" italics="true" pageId="20" pageNumber="2802">Bombilactobacillus mellifer</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[637,756,799,823]" pageId="20" pageNumber="2802" rank="species">comb. nov</taxonomicNameLabel>
; 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Zheng &amp; Wittouck &amp; Salvetti &amp; Franz &amp; Harris &amp; Mattarelli &amp; O’Toole &amp; Pot &amp; Vandamme &amp; Walter &amp; Watanabe &amp; Wuyts &amp; Felis &amp; Gänzle &amp; Lebeer" authorityYear="2020" box="[121,321,829,853]" class="Bacilli" family="Lactobacillaceae" genus="Bombilactobacillus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Bacteria" order="Lactobacillales" pageId="20" pageNumber="2802" phylum="Firmicutes" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[121,321,829,853]" italics="true" pageId="20" pageNumber="2802">Bombilactobacillus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was previously referred to as 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Zheng &amp; Wittouck &amp; Salvetti &amp; Franz &amp; Harris &amp; Mattarelli &amp; O’Toole &amp; Pot &amp; Vandamme &amp; Walter &amp; Watanabe &amp; Wuyts &amp; Felis &amp; Gänzle &amp; Lebeer" authorityYear="2020" baseAuthorityName="Zheng &amp; Wittouck &amp; Salvetti &amp; Franz &amp; Harris &amp; Mattarelli &amp; O’Toole &amp; Pot &amp; Vandamme &amp; Walter &amp; Watanabe &amp; Wuyts &amp; Felis &amp; Gänzle &amp; Lebeer" baseAuthorityYear="2020" box="[651,759,829,853]" class="Bacilli" family="Lactobacillaceae" genus="Bombilactobacillus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Bacteria" order="Lactobacillales" pageId="20" pageNumber="2802" phylum="Firmicutes" rank="species" species="mellifer">
<emphasis box="[651,759,829,853]" italics="true" pageId="20" pageNumber="2802">L. mellifer</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
group.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
